{\centerline}{\bf  Abstract}
We introduce the deformed fermionic numbers, corresponding to the skein relations,
the main characteristics of knots and links. These fermionic numbers allow one
to restore the skein relations.
For the Alexander (Jones) skein relation we introduce  corresponding Alexander (Jones) fermionic
$q$-numbers, and for the HOMFLY skein relation -- the HOMFLY deformed $(p,q)$-numbers with
one fermionic parameter.


\vspace{0.3cm}
\noindent
{\bf Keywords:} knots and links; Alexander, Jones, HOMFLY skein relations; polynomial invariants; recurrence relation;
deformed fermionic numbers.

